# Local RSA-2048 key whose public half is baked into `manifest.json#key`.
# The committed key in the manifest is enough for Chrome to derive the
# stable dev extension ID; the private key only matters if you ever pack
# a .crx, which we don't do in dev. Keep it out of git so the repo never
# carries an unencrypted private key.
.dev-key.pem
